About
-----

These scripts help you build you a full virtual box or EC2 virtual machine complete with a working buddycloud instance.
The scripts automatically setup and install the followign buddycloud components:

- buddycloud server
- buddycloud webclient
- apache and virtual host config
- database
- XMPP server

This instance should run fine as an EC2 macine on Amazon's micro instance
- http://aws.amazon.com/free/
- http://aws.amazon.com/ec2/#pricing

Install the prereqs
-------------------

apt-get install rubygems puppet virtualbox virtualbox-ose dkms linux-headers-$(uname -r)
gem install veewee vagrant

Building a buddycloud dev vm
----------------------------

vagrant basebox build buddycloud
vagrant basebox export buddycloud
vagrant up
vagrant ssh

Setting up your new image on AWS
--------------------------------

https://buddycloud.org/wiki/Buddycloud_on_Amazon_Web_Service
